Job Description
 Use efficiently our growing partner network to connect with startup founders and HRs, contribute to the network expansion (e.g. Co-working spaces, accelerators, chamber of commerce,  high tech park, entrepreneurs’ communities);
 Identify and validate effective ways to connect with entrepreneurs and raise their interest to learn more about StartupCare ;
 Master basics on health ecosystem, health management solution, employee benefits and FAQs;
 Deliver presentation; co-organize offline events for market education, partnership proposal, etc.
 Work together with marketing team to put forth promotional materials/tools and marketing events desired by startup founders and HRs;
 Reach weekly lead generation and quarterly sales target;
 Be well acquainted with startup environment and ecosystem in China;
 Keep skills and knowledge up to date by constantly participating in educational opportunities, reading professional 
 publications, growing and maintaining personal network.
      
 Knowledge & Experience
 Bachelor degree required
 3+ years professional experience in commercial and/or business development areas related to startup ecosystem;   
 Willing to learn, striving for improving and achieving results, strong communication and interpersonal skills;
 Work well under pressure, capable of handling multiple tasks with good time management skills;
 Team player > being able to coordinate with multiple cross functional teams to deliver the result, start-up environment > willing to go “extra mile” to achieve a success;
 Adopts methodical approach, combined with creativity, determination and persistence – innovation driven;
 Excellent verbal and written communication skills in Chinese and good level of English;

岗位职责： 
 负责用户画像，推荐算法和机器学习平台的搭建;
 改进产品的资讯内容推荐系统，优化用户的阅读体验;
任职要求：1、三年以上互联网工作经验，对自然语言处理、图像语音、广告、推荐系统等任何一个领域有实践经验； 2、对机器学习系统有一定了解；熟悉最优化的基础理论，能够将业务问题转化成相关的优化问题并求解，深刻理解并独立实现过相关算法（回归、决策树、分类问题、深度神经网络、图模型，概率统计，最优化方法等） 3、熟悉常用数据结构，具备扎实的算法基本功，熟悉C++、Python、go等编程语言；编程能力强，代码爱好者加分。 4、良好的业务理解能力和逻辑思维能力，能够从海量数据中发现关键特征，出色的问题分析及解决能力
